https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500null This documentary follows the 2004 Missouri Democratic primary to replace retiring 28-year veteran and former House Majority Leader Dick Gephardt. It is told from inside the campaign of Jeff Smith, a 29-year old part-time political science instructor at Washington University. Can Mr. Smith Get to Washington Anymore?
